These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
City: paris, marseilles, miami, colone, hamburg
There are 5 different nationalities: brazilian, british, chinese, pakistani, russian
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, bongani, ritmeester, vegafina, bluemaster
5 different games are played: poker, chess, bridge, scrabble, snooker
 1. the person playing bridge is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 2. the person playing snooker is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 3. the person playing chess is on the right of the brazilian##1
 4. the person playing poker is on the right of the chinese##1
 5. the bongani-smoker is the pakistani##1
 6. the british is the person traveling to marseilles##1
 7. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 8. the british is on the far left##1
 9. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the british##1
10. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person playing poker##1
11. the bongani-smoker is the person playing poker##1
12. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| City         | marseilles  | paris    | colone | miami    | hamburg  |
| Nationality   | british  | brazilian | chinese | pakistani | russian  |
| Cigar           | bolivar     | bluemaster     | vegafina  | bongani   | ritmeester    |
| Game         | bridge | scrabble    | chess | poker  | snooker |

