.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: ivory, lilac, coral, aquamarine, fuchsia
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, game, blend, ritmeester, pall-mall
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, documentary, family, martial-arts
5 different pets are kept: rat, horse, lizard, snake, turtle
 1. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 2. the owner of the lizard is the person watching animation movies##1
 3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 4. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 6. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 8. the person who likes coral is the person watching documentary movies##1
 9. the owner of the snake is the person who likes coral##1
10. the person who likes lilac is in the middle##1
11. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
12. the person who likes coral is the game-smoker##1
13. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Color          | coral        | fuchsia | lilac     | aquamarine      | ivory  |
| Cigar           | game   | blend | pall-mall    | ritmeester | havana |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | family     | martial-arts | adventure    | animation  |
| Pet   | snake     | horse | rat    | turtle      | lizard    |

