The people prefer 5 different music-genres: d&b, techno, jazz, blues, reggae
 1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 3. the dannemann-smoker is in the middle##1
 4. the cottage house is in the middle##1
 5. the old-henry-smoker is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
 7. the fan of blues is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 8. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
 9. the fan of reggae is in the middle##1
10. the fan of jazz is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
11. the old-henry-smoker is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
12. the art-deco house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
13. the colonial house is the davidoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
