 3. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person watching horror movies##1
 4. the owner of the fish is the person watching drama movies##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
 6. the person playing chess is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 7. the person playing go is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is in the middle##1
 9. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
10. the person who likes apricot is the owner of the goat##1
11. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
12. the person playing billiard is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
