 9. the fan of pop is the person who's birthday is in march##1
10. the fan of r&b is in the middle##1
11. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
12. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
13. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
14. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
