.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-17::.
House: cottage, palace, gothic-revival, farmhouse, futuristic
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: lily, azalea, sunflower, poppy, iris
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, country, folk, house, reggae
The people use 5 different means of transport: bus, airplane, van, car, trike
 1. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
 2. the cottage house is on the far left##1
 3. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the fan of blues##1
 4. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the fan of country##1
 5. the person who growslily is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 6. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 7. the person who growsazalea is the person driving the bus##1
 8. the fan of blues is on the left of the person who growslily##1
 9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
10. the futuristic house is on the right of the palace house##1
11. the person driving the car is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
12. the person who growssunflower is the fan of house##1
13. the person who growsiris is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| House      | cottage      | palace       | futuristic         | farmhouse  | gothic-revival |
| Flower   | sunflower  | poppy | azalea | lily  | iris  |
| Music-Genre   | house    | country    | blues        | reggae | folk     |
| Transport           | airplane | van      | bus       | car   | trike   |

