.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-18::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, crime, sports, thriller, western
The people use 5 different means of transport: trike, boat, snowmobile, subway, taxi
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: orchid, bellflower, aconite, iris, lily
5 different games are played: domino, snooker, scrabble, canasta, monopoly
 1. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 3. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 4. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 5. the person who growslily is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 6. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 7. the person watching crime movies is the person playing domino##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is the person driving the boat##1
 9. the person who growsbellflower is in the middle##1
10. the person who growsorchid is the person driving the taxi##1
11. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
12. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
13. the person watching thriller movies is the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |     5     |
