.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-19::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, lemonade, milk, tea
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: lily, aconite, daffodil, iris, dahlia
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: soccer, snowboarding, weightlifting, swimming, handball
There 5 different types of food: onion, strawberry, raspberry, blueberry, watermelon
 1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 2. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 3. the person who growsdahlia is the person eating onion##1
 4. the person eating raspberry is on the far right##1
 5. the person eating strawberry is the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
 8. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating onion##1
 9. the person eating onion is in the middle##1
10. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
11. the person who growslily is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
12. the person who growsdaffodil is the person drinking tea##1
13. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4    |   5    |
