.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-20::.
5 different games are played: domino, poker, bridge, backgammon, snooker
The people have 5 different hobbies: skydiving, collecting, hiking, video-games, camping
City: rome, san-francisco, colone, boston, new-york
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, scooter, snowmobile, train, tram
 1. the person playing bridge is in the middle##1
 2. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person driving the helicopter##1
 3. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person traveling to new-york##1
 5. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
 6. the person driving the train is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 7. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 8. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 9. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person playing domino##1
10. the person playing poker is on the far left##1
11. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1
12. the person who's hobby is camping is in the middle##1
13. the person traveling to rome is the person playing backgammon##1
14. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3    |     4      |   5    |
| Game      | poker | backgammon   | bridge    | domino       | snooker |
| Hobby   | hiking           | collecting   | camping   | video-games       | skydiving  |
| City   | san-francisco       | rome | colone | boston     | new-york   |
| Transport     | snowmobile    | scooter   | train   | helicopter | tram   |

 